<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布洛姆市长还在大口喘气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15001</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探站起来，让市长坐下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“告诉我发生了什么，市长。” 史密斯侦探说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布洛姆市长深吸了一口气：“我在办公室工作，突然冲进来一群猿猴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35010</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们穿着盔甲，拿着各种武器！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41550</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只猿猴——也许是长臂猿，它说孙悟空现在是美罗城的王！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41822</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47206</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后孙悟空走进来，坐在我的座位上！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47206</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有人能占领我们的城市！” 史密斯侦探卷起袖子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54405</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去看看！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54405</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>市政府周围有了巨大的城墙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猿猴们拿着武器站在城墙上，看起来很危险。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探找到了一扇门，他敲了敲门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大门打开，一只大猩猩走了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你有什么事儿？” 大猩猩问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86198</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探清了清嗓子：“我想和孙悟空谈谈。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86198</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大猩猩哼了一声：“跟我来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，史密斯侦探来到布洛姆市长的办公室。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100746</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空坐在办公桌前，八戒站在他旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100746</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大猩猩瞪着史密斯侦探：“见到国王要行礼！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在开玩笑吗？” 史密斯侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112459</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“美罗城没有国王。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁边的猿猴们非常惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118858</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没关系。” 悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“史密斯侦探没见过国王，这次就原谅他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128827</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的军队是从哪儿来的？” 史密斯侦探问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132060</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们是从花果山来的。” 悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那里是我的另一个王国。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>对了，你喜欢我在这栋楼周围建的城墙吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是我用一根头发变的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143298</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯眯起眼睛：“你不能这样占领这个城市！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152479</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空耸了耸肩：“我当然可以。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152479</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒走上来，笑了笑：“来人！把这个人关进监狱！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们会开一个盛大的宴会！” 黑雨大王说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他和小妖们一起在厨房。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个小妖在切菜，几个小妖在做香料，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有两个小妖准备了一大盆盐水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182965</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大王。” 一个小妖说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182965</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们先去腌那个紫色的怪物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑雨大王拍了拍肚子：“听起来很美味！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195495</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，有人敲门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195495</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200012</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大王，要我去开门吗？” 一个小妖问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200012</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204072</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我去看看。” 黑雨大王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204072</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210080</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可能是那个讨厌的女神仙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210080</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213700</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑雨大王打开门看到了山神。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213700</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，是你。” 他说，“你来做什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“让我进去说吧。” 山神说，“我有重要的消息告诉你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233679</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑雨大王让她进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233679</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他伸出头看了看周围，然后砰的一声关上了门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241883</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门锁咔嚓落下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241883</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245221</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了，你要跟我说什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245221</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254496</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>山神看起来很担心：“我刚才在跟一个女神仙说话，她真的很生你的气。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254496</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑雨大王耸了耸肩：“所以呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她说她要来这里。” 山神说，“她要救唐僧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，是吗？” 黑雨大王眯起眼睛，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270207</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274926</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会做好准备等着她！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>